<img src="http://pic1.zhimg.com/042299fa4_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="http://pic1.zhimg.com/042299fa4_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$pirate-henry" href="/people/pirate-henry">Pirate Henry</a>，<strong title="Mind Hacker，Computational Neuroscience Researcher，爱写知乎夜用加长版答案" class="zu-question-my-bio">Mind Hacker，Computational Neuroscienc…</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="4">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$fanny-64" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/fanny-64" class="zg-link" title="Fanny">Fanny</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zeepen" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zeepen" class="zg-link" title="Zeepen">Zeepen</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$xiaoqiangzhao" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/xiaoqiangzhao" class="zg-link" title="赵小强">赵小强</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
